item.content:encoded:
you know its funny to see rinty here, lee duncan is my great uncle. and his daughter carolyn, and my mom, there job in the fifties was trans porting rinty. the even did a hit and run once up here in big bear denting "nellie-bell" roy rogers jeep. the real funny bit is i have a scar on my but where i was bitten buy rinty aka flash, the tv dog. all the “rin-tin-tin” dogs were owned and trained buy the duncan familiy till this group in texas stole the name and copy wrighted it.
jean karwelis
bunker hill is worth the effort
